  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个状态流转图，描述工作节点的生命周期。核心状态有两个：静止状态和运动状态。另外还要考虑异常终止的情况。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Still和Moving之间可以互相转换。Crash是从Moving进入的吗？还有，这些状态跟基础设施组件有交互吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Crash只能从Moving进入。另外系统依赖三个基础设施：Redis缓存作为入口，Etcd集群用于故障恢复，WorkerNode是实际载体。静止状态可以直接调度到工作节点上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把基础结构画出来：RedisCache指向Still作为入口，Still分出两条线——一条到WorkerNode表示调度，一条到Moving表示状态切换。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Still",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "这部分没问题。Moving要能回到Still，也要能进入Crash。Crash之后必须由Etcd集群接管恢复。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Still",
        "Crash",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了：Moving到Still的返回路径，Moving到Crash的异常路径，以及Crash指向EtcdCluster的恢复链路。图已经完整了，您看看流转关系对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Still",
        "Crash",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Crash到EtcdCluster的箭头方向反了。应该是Crash指向EtcdCluster，表示故障上报给集群，不是集群指向Crash。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Crash",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，箭头现在从Crash指向EtcdCluster。整个状态图确认无误：RedisCache入口→Still→分支到WorkerNode或Moving→Moving可回退或异常→Crash上报EtcdCluster。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Still",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
